Date: 1995-03-03

Title: Braid Relations in Affine Toda Field Theory

Authors: A.Fring

Comments: 20 pages Latex

Journal-ref: Int.J.Mod.Phys. A11 (1996) 1337-1352

We provide explicit realizations for the operators which when exchanged giverise to the scattering matrix. For affine Toda field theory we present twoalternative constructions, one related to a free bosonic theory and the otherformally to the quantum affine Heisenberg algebra of $U_q(\hat{Sl_2})$.